{"tid":927174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"住家外有人大規模示威　老婦關窗時慘遭催淚彈擊中身亡","createTime":"2018-12-04T03:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T04:59:52.000Z","uid":121473,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ef767c359250c976dd26634dff2f624a8cb7a6dd","tid":927174,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NYny3Zz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYny3Zz.jpg&h=4ca787db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬賽市的反政府示威活動演變成暴力衝突。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n法國各地近日陸續出現大規模反政府示威活動，民眾穿著黃背心上街抗議徵收燃油稅等政策。多地示威遊行演變成暴力衝突，住在馬賽的一位老太太，就因為被窗外飛來的催淚彈罐擊中，送醫後不治身亡。<br />\n <br />\n當地媒體報導，法國第二大城馬賽周六也出現「黃背心」示威活動，一位住在示威地點附近的80歲老太太，正準備關窗時，突然被一枚催淚彈擊中臉部。老太太立刻被送醫急救，但在急救過程中不幸休克死亡。目前不確定擊中老太太的催淚彈來自警方或示威者。<br />\n <br />\n法國警方表示，自反政府示威活動2周前展開以來，已有3人死亡。另據法國內政部表示，全國約有13萬6千人於周日走上街頭參加示威遊行，抗議政府大幅調漲燃油稅。<br />\n <br />\n「黃背心」示威被視為法國自1968年以來最嚴重的暴力反政府活動，又以法國首都巴黎受創最大。法國總統馬克宏（Emmanuel Macron）自G20峰會返國後，立刻前往示威地凱旋門前發表演說譴責暴力。然周一有更多團體加入示威活動，「黃背心」運動目前尚無結束跡象。（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181204/1477756/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181204%2F1477756%2F&d=woWKBtP6PCnvw6rWWJT%2B2gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=8ae05900\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181204%2F1477756%2F&h=f566c540\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181204/1477756/</a>"},{"pid":"890bcea03c5f11f0dd9cf95bb549ced427c41243","tid":927174,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4b3eb853b35b839d500139abf6d19d78e75e42","tid":927174,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084de07766e852edab3f8b779647d9a9e10f76b8","tid":927174,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"如果係法國政府就仆街囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c88472ada26428e39690c1034da8b2cd7cc21f","tid":927174,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"普通人會有催淚彈咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271f67db896add0a27bb9d4880229b21d3815852","tid":927174,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"084de07766e852edab3f8b779647d9a9e10f76b8","tid":927174,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"如果係法國政府就仆街囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"唔撚出催淚彈，由班暴徒放火,打爛玻璃,打家劫舍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb03996ab78fe62e2e9106edb70e9a87d5acb790","tid":927174,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"In your face haha"},{"pid":"f44717ae8874f8612bb6daab469315ca1a6de728","tid":927174,"uid":34666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"271f67db896add0a27bb9d4880229b21d3815852","tid":927174,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"084de07766e852edab3f8b779647d9a9e10f76b8","tid":927174,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"如果係法國政府就仆街囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"唔撚出催淚彈，由班暴徒放火,打爛玻璃,打家劫舍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:59:52.000Z","msg":"唔撚出汽油彈，由馬克龍班暴君打家劫舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}